\title{ggpaintr: Formula-Driven ggplot Shiny Apps}
\description{
\code{ggpaintr} turns a single ggplot-like formula string into a small Shiny app
with generated controls, rendered plots, generated code, inline runtime
feedback, upload support for \code{.csv} and \code{.rds} files, copy customization, and
per-app custom placeholder registries. It also provides lower-level helpers
for runtime inspection, standalone app export, and column-name normalization
for data used with the built-in \code{var} placeholder.
